{"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/flyhud.FlyHUD\/documentation\/FlyHUD"]]},"metadata":{"role":"article","roleHeading":"Article","title":"Advanced Features","modules":[{"name":"FlyHUD"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"Animation-System","text":"Animation System","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"FlyHUD provides a rich animation system for showing and hiding the HUD."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"animation-states.svg"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"Animation-Styles","text":"Animation Styles"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Configure via ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/flyhud.FlyHUD\/documentation\/FlyHUD\/HUD\/Animation-swift.struct","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":":"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Fade (default)","HUD.show(to: view, using: .animation(.fade))","","\/\/ Zoom in when appearing, zoom out when disappearing","HUD.show(to: view, using: .animation(.zoomInOut))","","\/\/ Slide up when appearing, slide down when disappearing","HUD.show(to: view, using: .animation(.slideUpDown))"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Available styles:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"header":"row","type":"table","rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Style","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":".none","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No animation"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":".fade"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Opacity transition"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":".zoomInOut"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Zoom in on show, zoom out on hide","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":".zoomOutIn"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Zoom out on show, zoom in on hide"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":".zoomIn","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Always zoom in","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":".zoomOut"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Always zoom out","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":".slideUpDown"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Slide up on show, slide down on hide","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":".slideDownUp","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Slide down on show, slide up on hide","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":".slideUp","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Always slide up"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":".slideDown","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Always slide down","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":".slideRightLeft","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Slide right on show, slide left on hide"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":".slideLeftRight","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Slide left on show, slide right on hide","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":".slideRight","type":"codeVoice"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Always slide right"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":".slideLeft"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Always slide left","type":"text"}]}]]]},{"level":3,"text":"Spring Damping","anchor":"Spring-Damping","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Add bounce effects with spring damping:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Default damping (0.65)","HUD.show(to: view, using: .animation(.zoomInOut, damping: .default))","","\/\/ Custom damping ratio (lower = more bounce)","HUD.show(to: view, using: .animation(.slideUpDown, damping: .ratio(0.5)))","","\/\/ No damping (smooth deceleration)","HUD.show(to: view, using: .animation(.fade, damping: .disable))"]},{"level":3,"text":"Animation Duration","anchor":"Animation-Duration","type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["HUD.show(to: view, using: .animation(.fade, duration: 0.5))"]},{"level":3,"text":"Per-Hide Animation","anchor":"Per-Hide-Animation","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Override animation when hiding:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["let hud = HUD.show(to: view, using: .animation(.slideUp))","","\/\/ Hide with a different animation","hud.hide(using: .animation(.slideDown))"]},{"level":2,"text":"Keyboard Layout Guide (iOS)","anchor":"Keyboard-Layout-Guide-iOS","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"FlyHUD can automatically adjust its position when the keyboard appears."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"text":"Global Configuration","anchor":"Global-Configuration","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Set once in ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AppDelegate"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SceneDelegate"},{"text":":","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Center HUD in the visible area above keyboard","HUD.keyboardGuide = .center()","","\/\/ Center with vertical offset","HUD.keyboardGuide = .center(-20.0)","","\/\/ Keep content bottom above keyboard","HUD.keyboardGuide = .bottom(8.0)"]},{"level":3,"text":"Per-Instance Configuration","anchor":"Per-Instance-Configuration","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Override the global setting for individual HUDs:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["let hud = HUD.show(to: view, label: \"Verifying...\")","hud.keyboardGuide = .center()"]},{"level":3,"text":"Keyboard Guide Modes","anchor":"Keyboard-Guide-Modes","type":"heading"},{"header":"row","type":"table","rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Mode"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Behavior"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":".disable"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No keyboard tracking (default)"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"code":".center(offsetY)","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Center HUD in visible area above keyboard"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":".bottom(spacing)"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Position content bottom relative to keyboard top"}]}]]]},{"name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Keyboard guide is only available on iOS. It has no effect on tvOS or visionOS."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","type":"aside"},{"text":"Grace Time","level":2,"anchor":"Grace-Time","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following diagram illustrates how "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"graceTime"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"minShowTime"},{"type":"text","text":" interact:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"grace-time.svg"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Prevent HUD from appearing for very short tasks:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["let hud = HUD(with: view)","hud.graceTime = 0.5  \/\/ Don't show if task completes within 0.5s","view.addSubview(hud)","hud.show()","","\/\/ If hide() is called within 0.5s, HUD never appears","DispatchQueue.main.asyncAfter(deadline: .now() + 0.3) {","    hud.hide()  \/\/ HUD was never shown","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"name":"Important","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"graceTime"},{"text":" must be set before calling ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"show()"},{"text":". The convenience","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"HUD.show(to:)"},{"text":" does not support grace time — use manual initialization instead.","type":"text"}]}],"style":"important","type":"aside"},{"text":"Minimum Show Time","level":2,"anchor":"Minimum-Show-Time","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Prevent HUD from flickering by enforcing a minimum display duration:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let hud = HUD(with: view)","hud.minShowTime = 1.0  \/\/ Show for at least 1 second","view.addSubview(hud)","hud.show()","","\/\/ Even if hide() is called immediately, HUD stays for 1s","hud.hide()"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Activity Count","anchor":"Activity-Count","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"activity-count.svg"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Track multiple show\/hide pairs with a reference counter:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let hud = HUD.show(to: view)","hud.isCountEnabled = true","","\/\/ Each show increments count","hud.show()  \/\/ count = 2","hud.show()  \/\/ count = 3","","\/\/ Each hide decrements count; HUD hides only when count reaches 0","hud.hide()  \/\/ count = 2, still visible","hud.hide()  \/\/ count = 1, still visible","hud.hide()  \/\/ count = 0, hides"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This is useful when multiple subsystems independently request the HUD."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Event Delivery","anchor":"Event-Delivery","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Control whether touches pass through the HUD overlay:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Default: HUD blocks all touches","hud.isEventDeliveryEnabled = false","","\/\/ Allow touches outside contentView to pass through","hud.isEventDeliveryEnabled = true"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When enabled, only touches within the content card are captured by the HUD."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Touches in the surrounding overlay area pass through to the parent view."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Layout Configuration","anchor":"Layout-Configuration","level":2},{"type":"heading","text":"Offset","anchor":"Offset","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Position the HUD content relative to center:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Bottom of screen","hud.layout.offset = .h.vMaxOffset","","\/\/ Top of screen","hud.layout.offset = .h.vMinOffset","","\/\/ Centered (default)","hud.layout.offset = .zero"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Edge Insets","anchor":"Edge-Insets","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Set minimum distance from HUD edges:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["hud.layout.edgeInsets = UIEdgeInsets(top: 40, left: 20, bottom: 40, right: 20)"]},{"type":"heading","text":"Safe Area","anchor":"Safe-Area","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Control whether safe area insets are respected:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["hud.layout.isSafeAreaLayoutGuideEnabled = true  \/\/ Default"]},{"type":"aside","name":"Warning","style":"warning","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isSafeAreaLayoutGuideEnabled"},{"type":"text","text":" must be set before the first "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"show()"},{"type":"text","text":" call."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"anchor":"Content-View-Layout","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Content View Layout"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Fine-tune the content card’s internal layout:"}]},{"code":["\/\/ Margins between card edge and content","hud.contentView.layout.hMargin = 24.0","hud.contentView.layout.vMargin = 24.0","","\/\/ Spacing between elements","hud.contentView.layout.hSpacing = 12.0","hud.contentView.layout.vSpacing = 8.0","","\/\/ Minimum content size","hud.contentView.layout.minSize = CGSize(width: 100, height: 100)","","\/\/ Force square aspect ratio","hud.contentView.layout.isSquare = true","","\/\/ Text alignment","hud.contentView.layout.alignment = .leading"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Motion-Effects","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Motion Effects"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Add a parallax tilt effect to the content view:"}]},{"code":["hud.contentView.isMotionEffectsEnabled = true"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Subclassing","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Subclassing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"HUD"},{"type":"text","text":" is an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"open"},{"type":"text","text":" class. Override "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"makeHUD(with:)"},{"type":"text","text":" to provide custom instances:"}]},{"code":["class MyHUD: HUD {","    override class func makeHUD(with view: UIView) -> HUD {","        let hud = MyHUD(frame: view.bounds)","        \/\/ Custom setup","        return hud","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}]}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Guides","generated":true,"anchor":"Guides","identifiers":["doc:\/\/flyhud.FlyHUD\/documentation\/FlyHUD\/custom-ui","doc:\/\/flyhud.FlyHUD\/documentation\/FlyHUD\/swiftui-integration","doc:\/\/flyhud.FlyHUD\/documentation\/FlyHUD\/best-practices","doc:\/\/flyhud.FlyHUD\/documentation\/FlyHUD\/testing"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/flyhud.FlyHUD\/documentation\/FlyHUD\/advanced-features","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"article","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/flyhud\/advanced-features"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Explore keyboard tracking, animations, grace time, activity counts, and more.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"references":{"doc://flyhud.FlyHUD/documentation/FlyHUD/best-practices":{"url":"\/documentation\/flyhud\/best-practices","identifier":"doc:\/\/flyhud.FlyHUD\/documentation\/FlyHUD\/best-practices","kind":"article","title":"Best Practices","type":"topic","role":"article","abstract":[{"text":"Recommended patterns for using FlyHUD effectively in production apps.","type":"text"}]},"activity-count.svg":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/flyhud.FlyHUD\/activity-count.svg","svgID":"my-svg","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":"State diagram showing activity count reference counter: Idle(0) → Active(1) → Active(2) → Active(3), decrements on hide(), HUD only hides when count reaches 0.","type":"image","identifier":"activity-count.svg"},"doc://flyhud.FlyHUD/documentation/FlyHUD/HUD/Animation-swift.struct":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Animation","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"HUD.Animation","url":"\/documentation\/flyhud\/hud\/animation-swift.struct","abstract":[],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Animation","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/flyhud.FlyHUD\/documentation\/FlyHUD\/HUD\/Animation-swift.struct"},"doc://flyhud.FlyHUD/documentation/FlyHUD/swiftui-integration":{"kind":"article","role":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/flyhud.FlyHUD\/documentation\/FlyHUD\/swiftui-integration","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Use FlyHUD declaratively in SwiftUI with the ","type":"text"},{"code":"FlyHUDSwiftUI","type":"codeVoice